dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents parcels for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase MilwaukeeCounty_Parcels_2016.gdb. The dataset was originally published by the Milwaukee County Land Information Office. [polygons representing tax parcels - one polygon per parcel identifier (TAXKEY) - polygons are 'stacked' to represent condominium parcels - includes property information attributes]
